title: Not Going To Make It
description:
It's been decided... Quantum Week Chris will not complete his "At A Theater Near Me" mission. Kirk has decided that Bill Belichick is the greatest coach in sports history. Hillary Clinton reads the speech she would have read in 2016 for a new MasterClass. A new Chris game, The Big Lead's Sports Media Awards & much more.
